Package core

Interface HlaObjectInstanceBase

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    HlaDynamicalEntity, HlaExecutionConfiguration, HlaHLAobjectRoot, HlaLauncher, HlaMoon, HlaPayload, HlaPhysicalEntity, HlaPhysicalInterface, HlaReferenceFrame
    public interface HlaObjectInstanceBase
    Base interface used by all object instances.

    This class is ThreadSafe as defined by Java Concurrency in Practice, see jcip.net.

      • isLocal

        boolean isLocal()
        Tells if this object instance is local or remote. An local instance is an instance that you have originally created.

        Returns:
        true if initialized

      • isWithinInterest

        boolean isWithinInterest()

        Returns:
        true if within interest.
